<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink379">
<l>taṉṉama rāyamoṭu naṉmaṇa nukarcciyi</l>
<l>ṉiṉitāṅ kollō taṉakkē paṉivarai</l>
<l>yiṉakkaḷiṟu vaḻaṅkuñ cōlai</l>
<l>vayakkuṟu veḷvē lavaṟpuṇarntu celavē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Is going along with the [man] with splendid white spear </l>
<l>[through] groves, where herds of elephants roam on dew mountains, </l>
<l>sweeter to her than enjoying a good marriage  </l>
<l>and the company of friends loving her? </l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
